{"tid":2053603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葛珮帆批評年輕人「自以為在爭取公義」 又突然「懺悔」：「呢一代年輕人好慘，我哋做得唔夠好」","createTime":"2020-06-06T12:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:28:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":31,"dislike":300,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"641b590b3724f0c400cdb80418077574c28fbcac","tid":2053603,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>葛珮帆突懺悔：我哋做得唔夠好</strong><br />\n<br />\n出席圓桌會議的包括警務處處長鄧炳強等嘉賓，以及多名民建聯成員。民<span style=\"color: red;\">建聯立法會議員葛珮帆指年輕人無底線，純粹呼喊口號就自以為在爭取公義</span>，「有邊個心中冇追求公平、公義同民主？但係咪用違法嘅手段追求？係咪燒死一個人就係良知？」她又批評部分家長將教育子女的責任全推到教師身上，「個個都覺得可以cross the line，大家圍爐話警察殺人強姦，話要用暴力打倒共產黨 。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">及後她突然「懺悔」指「呢一代年輕人好慘，我哋做得唔夠好，大家好忙好忙咁過每一日」</span>，指年輕人目光應放遠，「香港只係好細嘅城市，我哋有好大嘅祖國，唔想俾人話係輸出暴徒的城市。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074239&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2941bc1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074239&h=6d3c9965\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074239</a><br />\n影后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858b61a838baa366d1d494ff0adc6dd8888c4529","tid":2053603,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8015f891185ae7e78ce983718230682b3cf3aedd","tid":2053603,"uid":310700,"like":262,"dislike":2,"score":260,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkwSCQm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkwSCQm.jpg&h=6d67a1f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db93b5fcad64dd297e4a88b9139d5e2eca12aa62","tid":2053603,"uid":264245,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"精神分裂症"},{"pid":"4a9c0